node.text: Visiting the @sjpcollection Seaport District boutique and spending some time downtown. We have tons of sale items available, including some exclusives! Call 212-742-0359 and ask for Michael or come visit at 93 South Street. Ready to help and planning to be here once a week moving forward. Check in at @sjpcollection for details! X

node.text:
@caferiazor
It’s been too long. 
Pollo Riazor, sangria, delectable tapas and the gracious and hospitable servers and host add up to the perfect evening. It’s a neighborhood secret but don’t let that stop you from your own pilgrimage and making your own memories. 
Opened  in 1974 at 245 West 16th St in Chelsea, with 9 tables
Here’s to 47 more years!
X, SJ
Ps now double the tables indoor and plenty of outdoor seating as well!

node.text:
Thank you to everyone who has shared their enthusiasm and support for our production over the last LONG year and a half! 
We cannot wait to welcome you to the beautiful Hudson Theatre to see @plazasuitebway !!!!
Previews start Friday, February 25th, 2022 at @hudsonbway 
If you have any questions or concerns about previous or current ticket orders, please contact your point of purchase. For tickets purchased through the Hudson Theatre, please call (855)801-5876
And for new purchases you can go to plazasuitebroadway.com
We are ready at check-in!!!!
And very much looking forward to seeing you, at long last!!!! 
X,
SJ
